Package cnss.simulator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ApplicationAlgorithm
    The ApplicationAlgorithm interface should be implemented by any class whose instances are intended to implement the application running in nodes.
    ControlAlgorithm
    The ControlAlgorithm interface should be implemented by any class whose instances are intended to provide the routing algorithm.
